<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Strengthening Smart Contract Safety and Reliability</h3>



<p>By implementing Ethereum Improvement Proposals (EIPs), you can enhance the safety and reliability of smart contracts on the Ethereum network. Smart contracts are self-executing contracts with the terms of the agreement directly written into code. They automatically execute when certain conditions are met, eliminating the need for intermediaries.</p>



